                             'Inconnect' 1.0

                           by Charles-N. Jacob

  'Inconnect' is a @{" Workbench game " link play} where you have to link tiles of
the same type that are next to each other, either horizontally or
vertically.

  However, just to complicate things a little, sometimes the game
will randomly remove one or more links that already have been
made...

  Complete each game board in the least amount of moves.

  Have fun!

