@node play "The game: Installation/Playing"

                             Installation

  The installation is very simple, just place "Inconnect" where you
want on your hard drive, floppy disk, Ram Disk, etc. No other files
or Libraries are needed. However, the game requires a 68020(+)
Amiga with Workbench 2.0 or higher.

                             How to play?

  To play, just click on a tile, if there are tiles of the same
type next to it, they will link with the clicked tile.

  Sometimes, links that have previously been made will disappear,
so you will have to make the links again...

  Have fun!

  You can quit the game by clicking on the game window's close
button or by pressing on the 'Esc' key.

